[Student "S"]
{SOUTH's 3\H bid is "encouraging" so NORTH bids 4NT.

When SOUTH shows one Key Card, (an Ace), NORTH is afraid he may have a trump loser as well the 
other Ace. To find out about the \HQ he 
bids 5\D, the Queen Ask.

SOUTH has the \HQ but no King so she jumps 
to 6\H.}

